data.description: Welcome to your new home! This captivating residence boasts 4 bedrooms and 3.5 bathrooms, with an inviting open concept design. Situated on a corner lot in the highly sought-after Hunter's Bend neighborhood, this home offers a warm and spacious atmosphere.Upon entering, you'll be delighted by the elegant luxury vinyl plank flooring that graces the entire first level. To your right, you'll find a private home office with charming French doors, perfect for quiet work or study. As you continue down the hall, you'll step into the bright and airy living room, filled with natural light from numerous windows that overlook your expansive backyard. This space flows seamlessly into the well-appointed eat-in kitchen featuring a breakfast bar and stainless-steel appliances.From the kitchen, step outside to the large backyard, which is enclosed with a privacy fence, providing a serene and secluded space for relaxation. You can unwind on your patio, enjoying the peaceful surroundings. The first-floor master bedroom is a luxurious retreat, complete with an ensuite bathroom featuring dual vanities and a spacious walk-in shower. Upstairs, you'll discover two generous bedrooms that share a full bathroom, while the third bedroom on this level has its own ensuite, making it perfect for overnight guests. Additionally, a spacious loft area on the upper level serves as a versatile common space or playroom. This home offers the convenience of an excellent location, with easy access to Nexton, the interstate, and Volvo. Don't miss this opportunity to make this beautiful residence your new home!  A $1,500 Lender Credit is available and will be applied towards the buyer's closing costs and pre-paids if the buyer chooses to use the seller's preferred lender.  This credit is in addition to any negotiated seller concessions.
